data.text:
About

There are thousands of musicians around the world who do the hard work to create an original music. And other musicians who steal and reproduce.

Read more

Who is a copycat artist?

Copycat artist refer to a singer, music director or composer who adopts, copies, imitates, mimics, or steals the music of other artists .
